/// @noravexplora & @clubmaiteee catch up about the inspirational women in their lives highlighted through the personal touches to their upcoming signature colorways.

The Gazelle ADV by Nora & Samba ADV by Maité are available March 16th in select skate shops, online at adidas.com/skateboarding and on the adidas CONFIRMED app.
 
#adidasSkateboarding #IWD #InternationalWomensDay 
🎥 @torstenfrank @samuelmcguire

node.text:
No trips. No problem. @LucasPuig spends some quality time at home in Biarritz, France doing what he does best. Catch the PUIG landing in select skate shops and online at adidas.com/skateboarding September 19th.
•
#adidasSkateboarding #LucasPuig #LaMarqueAux3Bandes 🎥 @torstenfrank

node.text:
15-years of adidas x Busenitz /// “In a world of 15-seconds, 15-years is truly something special. I’m looking forward to another 15-years of fun with adidas Skateboarding through traveling, skating and making good shoes.” - Dennis Busenitz
•
The Busenitz Indoor Super is available in select skate shops and online at adidas.com/skateboarding
•
#adidasSkateboarding #DennisBusenitz

node.text:
Busenitz Indoor Super XV /// Celebrating 15-years with Dennis Busenitz. Guided by Busenitz’s creative vision and insights, the Busenitz Indoor Super takes cues from the past and introduces them to the present. The iconic Busenitz upper is merged with a vintage outsole inherited from an adidas indoor model from the 80s. The XV across the heels commemorates the 15-year anniversary of adidas x Busenitz. Available in select skate shops and online at adidas.com/skateboarding
•
#adidasSkateboarding #DennisBusenitz
